    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of medium-sized, high altitude mountain spruce native to western North America, from British Columbia and Alberta, Canada, to California, Arizona, and New Mexico, United States, with isolated populations also in Mexico.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
